    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AN EPIC UNEXPLORED Every mythology gets its game eventually. Greek. Norse. Egyptian. Chinese got Black Myth: Wukong. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ancient India has been waiting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029220/extras/5f2d9ad71bafcb27d15d130c7ab9973b.avif?t=1765567948\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029220/extras_big/5f2d9ad71bafcb27d15d130c7ab9973b.avif?t=1765567948 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dharmayuddha - The Righteous War, is an open world action RPG set during the Mahabharata—one of humanity's oldest and longest epics. No prior knowledge required. Just a world of gods, demons, and warriors unlike anything you've played.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029220/extras/bb89ac90e6c152b412ea41f88e230bb3.avif?t=1765567948\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029220/extras_big/bb89ac90e6c152b412ea41f88e230bb3.avif?t=1765567948 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DIVINE WEAPONS Astras are weapons blessed by the gods themselves. Fire that seeks its target. Lightning that chains between enemies. Arrows that never miss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But power has counters. Varunastra extinguishes Agneyastra. Water amplifies lightning. Wind disperses poison clouds. Every element reacts—use them together, use them against enemies, use the environment itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies wield astras too. Learn their patterns. Find their counters. Or be destroyed by the same divine power you command.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029220/extras/0baefbd029170236b330f30db2df1c59.avif?t=1765567948\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029220/extras_big/0baefbd029170236b330f30db2df1c59.avif?t=1765567948 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HUNT DEMONS. DUEL LEGENDS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face Rakshasas—demons of Hindu mythology—each designed as a unique encounter. Not procedural. Hand-crafted like fighting game bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge legendary warriors whose names echo through millennia. These aren't random enemies. They're duels that test everything you've learned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CHOICES THAT MATTER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn't good vs evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's duty vs desire. Family vs justice. Winning vs staying true to yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters remember. Alliances shift. Your reputation opens doors—and closes others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EXPLORE ANCIENT INDIA</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kingdoms at war. Sacred forests. Cities of gold. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ancient India deserves its epic.</p>",
